Around our resort, you will find that we have an outside area, a hotel packed with everything you could ever want, and a luxurious shopping mall!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Don't touch the buffet though, that's reserved for our beloved janitor!! Don't let him see you, for he won't forgive you for your mess. He’ll splash water on the whole place and then clean it all up, for you. Isn’t he lovely?

please don’t use the dark room. he doesn’t like it.

You may find that around the resort, there aren't any areas for sports, for any exhilarating activities. Do not fret! Remember, our resort is for complete tranquility... and maybe a bit of shopping along the way!

