== Entrances and Exits ==

==== '''Entrances''' ====

* Looping around the same fences in [[Level 204]] for an extended period of time will eventually make the wanderer fall through the ground into shrubbery on '''Level 189'''.
* Passing through multiple doorways in a short span of time in [[Level 206]] leads to the safe, dark room of this level.

==== '''Exits''' ====

* Using an elevator in '''The Hotel''' during [[Phenomenon 24]] will, once the doors slide open, bring one to [[Level 851]].
* Finding an imperfection in the level (other than delaminated paint) and restoring it to its original state will bring the wanderer to [[Level 37]].
* Watering any plant life on the level with [[Almond Water]] will bring the wanderer to a random low floor on [[Level 188.2]].
* At times, a false door, mimicking the safe red door, will appear in The Shopping Expanse. Pushing the false door open will bring one to [[Level Fun]]. One should remain cautious, as said doors are blood red over the crimson red of the usual doors.



